{"tid":700512,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友最近食藥減肥 我好擔心佢","createTime":"2018-06-13T11:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T17:33:53.000Z","uid":86629,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6bc044f413d8b1ddee89e6acd77718a08b981821","tid":700512,"uid":86629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T11:41:42.000Z","msg":"前幾日佢開始食一隻叫panbesy嘅藥減肥 咁我都google過下佢d side effect<br />\n發現呢隻藥根本冇乜益 唔食仲會反彈返<br />\n我有試過叫佢唔好食 佢又話之前試過 唔會有事嘅 <br />\n咁我都冇野好講啦 我又控制唔到佢食唔食<br />\n問題嚟啦 佢呢幾日身體都冇咩大礙 但情緒方面我諗隻藥對佢都好大影響<br />\n個人成日好煩躁 小小野就唔開心發我脾氣<br />\n今日仲扔爛左部電話<br />\n其實佢發我脾氣唔係問題 我冇所謂<br />\n但我驚佢再咁落去情緒低落真係會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76445588ce773e8778f9930842fd8ca2cd64a0e0","tid":700512,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:29:02.000Z","msg":"飛左去咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2ea66a3739683a1797a4fbfe4cae345c593c57","tid":700512,"uid":167536,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:16:49.000Z","msg":"食藥減肥既女= 走精面（初期最快見效）、唔肯付出（唔肯做運動、改善飲食）、on9無腦 (唔食即反彈）、易受人影響（人地話食藥有效就信）"},{"pid":"a0f6a4ab8d729ca2140a27c44731e007c26a0f6a","tid":700512,"uid":151664,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:52:39.000Z","msg":"無腦嘅女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲要暴燥發脾氣，送都唔屌！你擔心佢把撚咩？ 擔心吓自己幾時受唔住佢d 脾氣先啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaf3684152fa2c7304678606e906d2913f0003dc","tid":700512,"uid":44854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:54:03.000Z","msg":"我女朋友之前都係，人講佢就信<br />\n佢覺得試左冇壞，仲要上淘寶買。。。<br />\n真係唔驚食死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492fcf7cb232eb978c9ca43233dad2fe942b6434","tid":700512,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-